quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  17,103,"So he resolved to turn them out of the land (of Egypt). But We drowned him and all who were with him."
  17,104,"And We said to the Children of Israel after him: "
  17,105,"And with truth We have sent it down (i.e. the Qur’ân), and with truth it has descended. And We have sent you (O Muhammad صلى الله عليه و سلم) as nothing but a bearer of glad tidings (of Paradise for those who follow your Message of Islâmic Monotheism), and a warner (of Hell-fire for those who refuse to follow your Message of Islâmic Monotheism){1}.",1:[{17:105}]
  18,70,"He (Khidr) said: "
  18,71,"So they both proceeded, till, when they embarked the ship, he (Khidr) scuttled it. Mûsâ (Moses) said: "
  18,72,"He (Khidr) said: "
